{"tid":290583,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"人在摩洛哥，啲賊仔好猖狂","createTime":"2017-06-20T01:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T01:35:53.000Z","uid":32932,"like":380,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"716e66fbb463add1da5bba73f75176063e8cc698","tid":290583,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/090757_c3f0bc0f8965c25803758ded9dc7df7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F090757_c3f0bc0f8965c25803758ded9dc7df7a.jpg&h=7f95757d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/090834_9503273f60610e6fb6a0414b3d248912.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F090834_9503273f60610e6fb6a0414b3d248912.jpg&h=59356e2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食親飯都被圍攻，四、五隻係腳下，有大有細，有啲得手掌咁大，仲會係你腳附近打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁企起身要拎嘢食，最後我啲嘢食落晒班賊仔個肚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個肉醬意粉走左肉醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地仲好揀飲擇食，畀麵包佢地食，佢地會唔食，之後繼續眼望望，一副勁可憐嘅樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/090752_381fcee4e6ee901f6195f483ddae98f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F090752_381fcee4e6ee901f6195f483ddae98f5.jpg&h=4301ff5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咁跳上凳到，唔理佢嘅話會跳埋上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c1f6ba0b83c3532579dabe175d98a7281fd849","tid":290583,"uid":32932,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/091545_b4970759b856e070093820ccaf8a5ca7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http