-20T13:36:18.000Z","msg":"咁可愛嘅賊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n摩牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c727ae35c6c4f52eb1fab80d7c859cf4163be22e","tid":290583,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"我係你就唔好掂佢地了 我唔鐘意佢地爬入垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0410550219e153281e01ec103e8a9f1722e282a","tid":290583,"uid":62120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d428fc6da3c195b92eba51e4cdc95b37e6375bbc","tid":290583,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:10:09.000Z","msg":"好難忍到 唔比佢地 咁qq <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fcd612d3e6b9b23299436137a7cee32fef49ed","tid":290583,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好難忍到 唔比佢地 咁qq <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一隻貓我喂到畀職員stop<br />\n個侍應話佢地係廚房會喂 叫我唔好喂 <br />\n但你每食一啖，佢地就係你腳邊係咁喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好難唔喂<br />\n之後個侍應行埋黎，鋪左張墊枱紙係地下叫我如果想喂就放係紙上面 但個陣我已經食完+喂完"},{"pid":"f14edfb9f133d43368f61e92cbb9b784d8ae8d81","tid":290583,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T19:28:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好難忍到 唔比佢地 咁qq <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一隻貓我喂到畀職員stop<br />\n個侍應話佢地係廚房會喂 叫我唔好喂 <br />\n但你每食一啖，佢地就係你腳邊係咁喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好難唔喂<br />\n之後個侍應行埋黎，鋪左張墊枱紙係地下叫我如果想喂就放係紙上面 但個陣我已經食完+喂完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n麻煩到人喇<br />\n係咪衰呢"},{"pid":"90c6312cf55d2b57784d8863ee178fb5396b74fa","tid":290583,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T19:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好難忍到 唔比佢地 咁qq <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一隻貓我喂到畀職員stop<br />\n個侍應話佢地係廚房會喂 叫我唔好喂 <br />\n但你每食一啖，佢地就係你腳邊係咁喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好難唔喂<br />\n之後個侍應行埋黎，鋪左張墊枱紙係地下叫我如果想喂就放係紙上面 但個陣我已經食完+喂完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n麻煩到人喇<br />\n係咪衰呢</blockquote><br />\nd貓好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96bbcbfeca7918fc8e65ec2c9323bcd7c66853a","tid":290583,"uid":66340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T19:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/091545_b4970759b856e070093820ccaf8a5ca7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F091545_b4970759b856e070093820ccaf8a5ca7.jpg&h=9ca728d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/091548_d15ba5166d91a2c9a22ea2361268dc4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F091548_d15ba5166d91a2c9a22ea2